oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Real picture postcard image of musician Kenneth G. Redford
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This black and white image shows Musician, 3rd Class Kenneth G. Redford, 114th FA, HQ Co., 30th Div., in uniform standing in a field. The printing on the back of the postcard says carte postale, but there is no handwriting on the back.
